      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 577,
      "message": "(This comment is applicable all places where @gNBId is used.)\n\nThis is not the id of the GNBDUFunction MO. All 3gpp components must have the key named simply \"id\". GNBDUFunction is no exception.\nIt is defined so:\n\n augment \"/me3gpp:ManagedElement\" {\n\n    list GNBDUFunction {\n      key id;\n\n\nYou can check it in: https://forge.3gpp.org/rep/sa5/MnS/-/blob/Rel-19/yang-models/_3gpp-nr-nrm-gnbdufunction.yang",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 8121,
        "name": "Csaba Kocsis",
